title: Where are the patch notes for 5.16?
body: So i think i may be blind, but i am unable to find the patch notes for the upcoming patch. Is someone willing to lead the blind and show me??

replies.body: As it appears now, there seems to be no patch notes for 5.16 on the official website. I even tried using one of the links to 5.15 and "changing" the URL to what would be consistent with 5.16 and got error 404. Basically, this looks like on of those times where the patch notes will appear when the patch gets released.
Eww well, ill have to wait for it then. thanks anyway.

http://www.surrenderat20.net/p/516-pbe-cycle.html

These are PBE patch notes though, not always what goes on live (usually close and mostly the same though since the PBE is where they test patches).
